Package org.logevents.query

Class LogEventQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logevents.query.LogEventQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Predicate<LogEvent>
    public class LogEventQuery
extends Object
implements Predicate<LogEvent>
    Queries a list of LogEvent objects by time, interval, threadNames, loggers, level, markers, mdcFilter and nodeNames.

    Use test(LogEvent) to filter a Stream of LogEvents .
